                <div class="govuk-accordion__section">
                  <div class="govuk-accordion__section-header">
                    <h2 class="govuk-accordion__section-heading">
                      
                    <button type="button" id="accordion-default-heading-1a" aria-controls="accordion-default-content-2" class="govuk-accordion__section-button govuk-!-font-size-19" aria-expanded="false">
                        Critical success factors
                      <span class="govuk-accordion__icon" aria-hidden="true"></span></button></h2>
                  </div>
                  <div id="accordion-default-content-1a" class="govuk-accordion__section-content" aria-labelledby="accordion-default-heading-1a">
                    <p class="govuk-body-s">Critical success factors are elements in a project which are vitally important to achieving its goal.</p>
                    <p class="govuk-body-s">They are events or activities which need to be done to make a project successful.</p>
                    <p class="govuk-body-s">Every project will have different critical success factors.</p>
                    <p class="govuk-body-s">They could include:</p>
                    <ul class="govuk-body-s govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
                      <li>running a test in real-world environments</li>
                      <li>proving or disproving a theory</li>
                      <li>producing a working prototype</li>
                      <li>obtaining a patent</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="govuk-body-s">They should always be:</p>
                    <ul class="govuk-body-s govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
                      <li>specific</li>
                      <li>measurable</li>
                      <li>achievable</li>
                      <li>relevant</li>
                      <li>time-specific</li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </div>




                  <div class="govuk-accordion__section">
