                      <ul class="govuk-body-s govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
                        <li>alternative research and development (R&amp;D) approaches and why your approach is better</li>
                        <li>how important milestones depend on other factors in the project</li>
                        <li>major achievements you expect to reach</li>
                        <li>any points in the project where you will have to make go/no-go decisions</li>
                      </ul>
                    </div>
